If I leave my house at 6:52 am and run 1 mile at an easy pace (8:15 minutes per mile), 
then 3 miles at tempo (7:12 per mile) and 1 mile at easy pace again, what time do I get home for breakfast?


#turn time into seconds
start = (6*60 + 52)*60
easy_pace = 2* (8*60 +15)
tempo = 3 * (7*60 + 12)

total = (start + easy_pace + tempo)/(60*60) 
hours = int(total)
minutes = (total - hours)*60
minutes_only = int(minutes)
print("Breakfast will be at: ", hours, ":", minutes_only)
